{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place water into mixing bowl. Insert simmering basket, then weigh beetroot into it. Cook <nobr>35-40 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<\/nobr>, until beetroot is tender.","Remove simmering basket with aid of spatula and set beetroot aside to drain. Empty mixing bowl.","Place cooked beetroot into mixing bowl and chop <nobr>8 sec\/speed 4<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add butter, lemon juice, sugar and salt and cook <nobr>2 min\/100°C\/\/speed 2<\/nobr>.","Place a ceramic or glass bowl onto mixing bowl lid, then weigh sour cream into it. Add plain flour to sour cream and combine.","Add sour cream-flour mixture to mixing bowl and cook <nobr>3 min\/100°C\/\/speed 2<\/nobr>. Serve warm as a side dish."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["750 g water","500 g raw beetroot, peeled and cut into quarters","15 g salted butter","10 g lemon juice","1 tsp caster sugar","¼ tsp sea salt","50 g sour cream","1 tsp plain flour"]}],"id":"r97149","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-s2vCt2_VGpA\/XZWZbq9mXJI\/AAAAAAAAeM4\/MBDaXB8DVd0pCMAjkwqAnn3G9ALWBkpigCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_bQa1fpi2PwW1T3Z8.png","title":"Warm beetroot dish","publishedAt":"2015-05-18T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"2.5 g","fat":"8 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"11.6 g","calories":"568 kJ \/ 135 kcal"},"usefulItems":"ceramic or glass bowl","hintsAndTricks":["Serve as an accompaniment to beef, pork or chicken alongside mashed potatoes."],"basicInfo":["easy","5m","50m","4 portions"]}